From Danny Eldar Subject PBS Frontline documentary Memory of the camps Yesterday I watched an outstanding documentary on PBS prepared for Frontline by the documentary It is called Memory of the camps and shows some un censored pictures taken immediately after the liberation of Bergen Belsen and other death I recommend it to Check with your PBS station for re IT IS A MUST SEE In the Seatle Vancouver area KSTS will re broadcast the documentary on Monday You can also order a copy from PBS Video The cost is Danny